                        <h2>JAGDAMBA POLYMERS PRIVATE LIMITED</h2>
                        <p>We're the leading manufacturer of Plastic injection and blow moulded products, offers innovative and highest quality Plastic Houseware products, Plastic Moulded Furniture under the brand “Ankur”, besides PET Preforms and industrial & non-industrial custom moulded products. Our continuously growing large range of plastic consumer products is quite comprehensive, which meets the requirements and satisfaction of the customers in these segments. Constant R&D ensures introduction of new products at regular intervals.</p>
