               <p>The Brand “Ankur”, has gained trust and confidence of the consumers for over 20 years for its super quality, aesthetic, vibrant colours and many other attractive features.  Borne in Odisha, the brand “Ankur” is well established and one of the strongest in its segment in the region, gradually expanding pan India. The products are available in many states and will soon cover the length and breadth of the nation.</p> 

               <p>In existence for over two decades, Jagdamba Polymers has two manufacturing facilities, offering the most innovative and high-quality products with world class manufacturing facilities and latest technology. The raw material is sourced directly from established manufacturers backed with quality certificates and MSDS. Both manufacturing facilities are ISO 9001:2015 compliant, whereas the other unit is also FSMS 9001: 22000 (Food Safety) complaint. The Company also follows Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP) and aims to achieve TPM in due course of time. As a quality-oriented company, we offer the best products to our customers within their budgetary constraints.</p> 

               <p>Expansion of range of products is an ongoing process, whereby new products are introduced based on market research and demand. Household Products offers wide range of Kitchen, Table, bathroom, cleaning, Kids, etc. besides thermo-ware, PET Bottles & containers and injection and blow moulded products. Moulded Furniture offers, wide range of moulded chairs, Tables, stools and many other similar products.</p> 

               <p>We are a developing and progressive company and strive to grow faster. We believe in our mission and integrate them in our business practice. Jagdamba Polymers is a truly “ONE STOP SHOP” for plastic moulding solutions for all its customers</p> 
